    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Per-Client Traffic Limitation",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 22
      },
      "options": {
        "content": "### No Per-Client Bandwidth Here\nCurrent MKTXP + RouterOS API metrics do **not** expose upload/download counters per DHCP client IP.\n\nAccurate per-client traffic requires one of:\n- MikroTik Simple Queues per client\n- Traffic Flow / NetFlow collector\n- A custom queue/API collector designed for per-IP accounting\n\nThis dashboard shows aggregate LAN traffic only.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.2",
      "transparent": true
    }
